{"tid":722444,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"進退兩難","createTime":"2018-06-29T13:40:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T14:07:52.000Z","uid":183772,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f70332dcc3a2d3ba3a48d669703900f5e481b8fe","tid":722444,"uid":183772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T13:40:48.000Z","msg":"最近同個女仔行得埋左<br />\n佢同條仔啱啱散左,成日冇野做都係我陪佢,<br />\n關係自然越黎越好,睇戲都會挨下,攬下,拖下手<br />\n<br />\n但前排一同佢表完白,個關係就後退左步,佢話唔想咁快住...<br />\n依加雖然都係會陪住佢,但相處就冇之前咁近<br />\n<br />\n依加感覺就好似向前行左一大步,又後退番轉頭,行又行唔到落去,走又唔捨得走咁,點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4248902da1f74c878dc6734a612985da3def0de3","tid":722444,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T13:43:10.000Z","msg":"你個case係有退無進喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22ad230c2967469a69e6d371a03ae47f089cba5","tid":722444,"uid":183772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4248902da1f74c878dc6734a612985da3def0de3","tid":722444,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T13:43:10.000Z","msg":"你個case係有退無進喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T14:04:24.000Z","msg":"即刻直接走會好d?定再試下"},{"pid":"421a0e60525389e39d594d53f5c6941ae6dea26f","tid":722444,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f22ad230c2967469a69e6d371a03ae47f089cba5","tid":722444,"uid":183772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4248902da1f74c878dc6734a612985da3def0de3","tid":722444,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T13:43:10.000Z","msg":"你個case係有退無進喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T14:04:24.000Z","msg":"即刻直接走會好d?定再試下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T14:07:52.000Z","msg":"走啦<br />\n係同你一齊既表白個陣都一齊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}